thread.title_full: Aussie Vac @ Ducted Vacuum Centre reviewed by Paul Smith

author: Paul Smith
title: Paul Smith
text: I've used the Aussie Vac website a number of times over the years to reorder vacuum bags and purchase hose components. The website is easy to use and I've always received the products within a few days of order. Very happy.
